<div class="card-deck card-intro collapsed m-b-md">
    <div class="card text-center">
        <div class="card-block">
            <h3 class="card-title">队长</h3>
            <p class="card-text">如果你是队长，请在此注册队伍。</p>
            <div class="card-footer">
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="btn btn-sm btn-primary">开始注册</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card text-center">
        <div class="card-block">
            <h3 class="card-title">队员</h3>
            <p class="card-text">如果你是队员，请扫描队长提供的二维码进行认证，且每人只能参加一支队伍。误注册为队长的队员必须先取消注册再加入其他队伍。</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="card card-register">
    <div class="card-block">
        <div class="form-group">
            <h5>队长姓名</h5>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" value="{{user_name}}" disabled="disabled">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <h5>队长学号</h5>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" value="{{user_id}}" disabled="disabled">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <h5>班级 (F1XXXXXX)</h5>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" {{#with class_id}}value="{{this}}"{{/with}} placeholder="请如实填写">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <strong>队员信息</strong>
            <span class="float-right"><a href="javascript:void(0);" class="btn btn-sm btn-primary m-b-sm btn-add">添加队员</a></span>
            <table class="table">
                <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th width="30%">姓名</th>
                    <th width="40%">学号</th>
                    <th width="15%" class="text-center">已认证</th>
                    <th width="15%" class="text-center">操作</th>
                </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                {{#each member}}
                    <tr data-id="{{user_id}}">
                        <td>{{user_name}}</td>
                        <td>{{user_id}}</td>
                        <td align="center">{{#if verified}}<i class="fa fa-check"></i>{{/if}}</td>
                        <td align="center"><a class="btn-delete" href="javascript:void(0);"><i class="fa fa-trash"></i></a></td>
                    </tr>
                {{/each}}
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
        {{#if group_id}}
            <div class="form-group">
                <strong>请队长让所有组员扫描此二维码并使用JAccount登录认证</strong>
                <div class="qrcode m-t-sm"></div>
            </div>
        {{/if}}
        <div class="form-group text-center">
            <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="btn btn-primary btn-submit">提交</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>